{
  "page": "Simon Toyne",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Toyne\" title=\"House Toyne\"><img alt=\"House Toyne.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/27/House_Toyne.svg/50px-House_Toyne.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/27/House_Toyne.svg/75px-House_Toyne.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/27/House_Toyne.svg/100px-House_Toyne.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Simon Toyne</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Toyne\" title=\"House Toyne\"><img alt=\"House Toyne.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/27/House_Toyne.svg/50px-House_Toyne.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/27/House_Toyne.svg/75px-House_Toyne.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/27/House_Toyne.svg/100px-House_Toyne.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Simon_Toyne_TheMico.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Simon Toyne TheMico.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/37/Simon_Toyne_TheMico.jpg/250px-Simon_Toyne_TheMico.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"354\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/37/Simon_Toyne_TheMico.jpg/375px-Simon_Toyne_TheMico.jpg 1.5x, /images/3/37/Simon_Toyne_TheMico.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Simon by TheMico</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Toyne\" title=\"House Toyne\">House Toyne</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Kingswood_Brotherhood\" title=\"Kingswood Brotherhood\">Kingswood Brotherhood</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stormlander\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Stormlander\">Stormlander</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">281&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Kingswood\" title=\"Kingswood\">Kingswood</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Simon Toyne</b> was the leader of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingswood_Brotherhood\" title=\"Kingswood Brotherhood\">Kingswood Brotherhood</a>, an <a href=\"/index.php/Outlaw\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Outlaw\">outlaw</a> group active during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Simon_Toyne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>According to Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a>, Simon was infamous.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Simon_Toyne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Simon was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Toyne\" title=\"House Toyne\">House Toyne</a>, a family fallen into disgrace after <a href=\"/index.php/Terrence_Toyne\" title=\"Terrence Toyne\">altercations</a> with <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>. Under Simon's leadership, the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingswood_Brotherhood\" title=\"Kingswood Brotherhood\">Kingswood Brotherhood</a> achieved no small measure of infamy as they kidnapped various nobles and evaded capture. According to Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a>, Simon entered a <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Steffon%27s_tourney\" title=\"Lord Steffon&#39;s tourney\">tourney at Storm's End</a> as a <a href=\"/index.php/Mystery_knight\" title=\"Mystery knight\">mystery knight</a>, where he was unhorsed by Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar Targaryen</a>; a semi-canon source, however, states that Barristan may have misremembered the tourney.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The forest folk of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingswood\" title=\"Kingswood\">kingswood</a> had looked to Simon and his outlaws for protection. When Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Arthur_Dayne\" title=\"Arthur Dayne\">Arthur Dayne</a> led a campaign into the forest, however, the <a href=\"/index.php/Sword_of_the_Morning\" title=\"Sword of the Morning\">Sword of the Morning</a> gained the support of these <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">smallfolk</a> by paying them for supplies, bringing their grievances to King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a>, and allowing them to gain some additional rights.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> When Barristan rescued Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Swann\" title=\"Jeyne Swann\">Jeyne Swann</a> and her <a href=\"/index.php/Septa\" title=\"Septa\">septa</a> from the outlaws, he defeated the <a href=\"/index.php/Smiling_Knight\" title=\"Smiling Knight\">Smiling Knight</a> and slew Simon.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Ulmer_of_the_Kingswood\" title=\"Ulmer of the Kingswood\">Ulmer of the Kingswood</a> has often told the men at <a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a> about his adventures with Simon and other outlaws from the Brotherhood.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Simon_Toyne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Simon_Toyne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Arstan Whitebeard</a> tells <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> of her brother <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar's</a> defeat of Simon in a <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Steffon%27s_tourney\" title=\"Lord Steffon&#39;s tourney\">tourney at Storm's End</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> reads in the <a href=\"/index.php/White_Book\" title=\"White Book\">White Book</a> about Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a>'s slaying of Simon, and he recalls his own experiences with the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingswood_Brotherhood\" title=\"Kingswood Brotherhood\">Kingswood Brotherhood</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Simon_Toyne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>At <a href=\"/index.php/Darry\" title=\"Darry\">Darry</a>, Jaime explains how Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Arthur_Dayne\" title=\"Arthur Dayne\">Arthur Dayne</a> had turned the <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">smallfolk</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingswood\" title=\"Kingswood\">kingswood</a> against Simon and his outlaws.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Simon_Toyne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>When he was young, <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">His Grace</a> rode brilliantly in a <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_at_Storm%27s_End\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tourney at Storm&#39;s End\">tourney at Storm's End</a>, defeating Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Baratheon\" title=\"Steffon Baratheon\">Steffon Baratheon</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Mallister\" title=\"Jason Mallister\">Jason Mallister</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Oberyn_Martell\" title=\"Oberyn Martell\">Red Viper</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>, and a <a href=\"/index.php/Mystery_knight\" title=\"Mystery knight\">mystery knight</a> who proved to be the infamous Simon Toyne, chief of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingswood_Brotherhood\" title=\"Kingswood Brotherhood\">kingswood outlaws</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Arstan Whitebeard</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The world was simpler in those days, Jaime thought, and men as well as swords were made of finer steel. Or was it only that he had been fifteen? They were all in their graves now, the <a href=\"/index.php/Arthur_Dayne\" title=\"Arthur Dayne\">Sword of the Morning</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Smiling_Knight\" title=\"Smiling Knight\">Smiling Knight</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Gerold_Hightower\" title=\"Gerold Hightower\">White Bull</a> and Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Lewyn_Martell\" title=\"Lewyn Martell\">Lewyn</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Oswell_Whent\" title=\"Oswell Whent\">Oswell Whent</a> with his black humor, earnest <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Darry\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Jon Darry\">Jon Darry</a>, Simon Toyne and his <a href=\"/index.php/Kingswood_Brotherhood\" title=\"Kingswood Brotherhood\">Kingswood Brotherhood</a>, bluff old <a href=\"/index.php/Sumner_Crakehall\" title=\"Sumner Crakehall\">Sumner Crakehall</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Simon_Toyne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_11\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 11\">Chapter 11</a>, Jaime II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_42\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 42\">Chapter 42</a>, Daenerys IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/So_Spake_Martin\" title=\"So Spake Martin\">So Spake Martin</a>: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/SSM/Entry/Some_Continuity_Oddities\">Some Continuity Oddities</a>, February 13, 2001</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\">4.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_30\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 30\">Chapter 30</a>, Jaime IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">5.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\">5.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\">5.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-3\">5.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_67\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 67\">Chapter 67</a>, Jaime VIII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos33.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_33\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 33\">Chapter 33</a>, Samwell II.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403183325\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.165 seconds\nReal time usage: 1.083 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1195/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10901/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 11030/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2004/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4115/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.310/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.59 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  996.636      1 -total\n 84.17%  838.897      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 83.99%  837.080      1 Template:Infobox\n  9.63%   95.978     10 Template:Ref\n  6.45%   64.325     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  5.77%   57.519      1 Template:References\n  4.70%   46.880     10 Template:Ref/core\n  4.14%   41.275      2 Template:Quote\n  1.73%   17.200      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.27%   12.660      1 Template:Date\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:2080-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403183324 and revision id 333925\n -->\n",
